title: Lantania

properties.name: description
properties.value: Lantania was a citizen from a settlement in Hallowvale. She was mentioned in the dusty scroll, a letter from her boyfriend, Sialathin, who promises her that they will escape over the River Salve soon.

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Lantania

Lantania was a citizen from a settlement in Hallowvale. She was mentioned in the dusty scroll, a letter from her boyfriend, Sialathin, who promises her that they will escape over the River Salve soon.
